snippet.title: Don't Look Down Itch.io Release
snippet.description:
Smash and shoot robots, dodge hazards, and dash through hidden rooms. Can you save the world from the robot that you created?
Don't Look Down is a virtual reality climbing game with platforming and action elements.
Available on https://catapultgames.itch.io/dont-look-down at 6pm EST 12/07/18
